      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Litro Gas said that it will distribute 50,000 domestic gas cylinders to all provinces today (14).",
        "The Chairman of Litro Muditha Peiris noted that gas distribution will continue for the Colombo district as well.",
        "NO Resignation Letter; Speaker considering option of President vacating his post"
